              <p
                class="mt-2 mb-6 line-clamp-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
              >
                Simple decluttering strategies that professional organizers
                swear by. Transform your space with these practical methods.
              </p>

              <button
                id="openModalBtn"
                class="mt-auto group/btn flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl text-slate-800 font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:border-black dark:text-white dark:border-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-black"
              >
                <span>Detail Kegiatan</span>
